        <h2>FAQs</h2>

        <h3>What is Delta's Black Friday sale, and when does it start? </h3>
        <p>Delta Airlines give lots of offers and discounts during various holidays, and the Black Friday sale is one of them. It usually starts around late July to early August and ends during Black Friday. The price of <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/delta-tickets.aspx">Delta Airlines tickets</a>  drops and is available at a very cheap cost. This sale is perfect for you if you are planning a trip with your family during Christmas or New Year. You will be able to take advantage of high discounts on the tickets. </p>
        <h3>What are the features of Delta SkyMiles? </h3>
        <p>Delta Airlines provides various memberships for their passengers, and Delta SkyMiles is one of them. It is a loyalty program for passengers who fly with Delta Airlines frequently. In this membership, the points are collected with each <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/best-day-to-book-a-flight-on-delta-airlines.aspx">Delta flight</a> and can be redeemed later for more reductions in the flight ticket price. SkyMiles's benefits include getting your first checked bag for free and being eligible for getting complimentary upgrades and special considerations at the airport. </p>
        <h3>What are the advantages of Delta Vacation packages? </h3>
        <p>A poorly planned vacation can cost a lot of money and consume your precious time. This is why Delta Airlines provide exclusive vacation packages. <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/delta-reservation-site.aspx">Delta Vacation</a> packages allow you to save time and money. An individual's essential needs are considered when creating the packages, and it is formed and planned accordingly. The list of covered services includes lodging, food and beverages, transportation, etc. </p>
        <p>The packages require a one-time payment, after which you don't have to pay a single penny for anything. Sometimes there might be changes in plans, for which you can cancel your vacation packages without extra charges. If the cancellation is made 24 hours before the vacation starts, then there might be a slight reduction in the refund for the last-minute cancellation. </p>
        <h3>How many classes does Delta Airlines provide? </h3>
        <p>Although being a low-cost airline, Delta Airlines is renowned for its excellent services. The airline is well known for its classes and offers extravagant amenities on board. They provide a total of four classes, or it might differ as per the aeroplane model. The first is a basic economy class with standard yet considerable amenities, but seats are not assigned until boarding. The second is business class, which is basically for business travel. </p>
        <p>First class comes third, and it is available for short-distance flights or domestic travel with all the luxurious amenities. The fourth and final class is the membership-based Delta One class, which is the most deluxe class available on Delta Airlines. With all the lavish facilities and complimentary services, these classes are available for international travel. </p>
